From 022f7fddaa69060e4b2cb7e03b13c7d84d44b941 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 23:18:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add drag-to-reorder on All Tasks with API persistence

- Add SortOrder column and PATCH /api/tasks/reorder endpoint
- Return tasks ordered by sortOrder from GET /api/tasks
- Assign sortOrder on create and sync reorder through offline queue
- Use manual list order on All Tasks with CDK drag-and-drop
- Support long-press pop-out drag on touch devices
